### 01. 멤버 초대 이메일 발송 (관리자/소유자 전용)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/workspaces/{{workspacePublicId}}/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invitee@letzcollab.xyz",
  "position": "디자이너"
}

### 03. 내 권한/직책 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/workspaces/{{workspacePublicId}}/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 04. 내 직책 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/workspaces/{{workspacePublicId}}/members/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPosition": "백엔드 개발자"
}

### 05. 타 멤버 권한/직책 수정 (관리자/소유자 전용)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/workspaces/{{workspacePublicId}}/members/{{targetUserPublicId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPosition": "프론트엔드 개발자",
  "newRole": "MEMBER"
}